  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Club Hotel Panorama is on an all inclusive board basis. Breakfast, lunch, evening meals and drinks are included.</p>
<p>Enjoy an extensive breakfast buffet with a variety of hot and cold options. Head back to the hotel at lunchtime to enjoy the lunch buffet with a range of choices. After the mountain has closed for the day, cosy up with a drink and enjoy a variety of sweet treats as an after ski snack. </p>
<p>Dinner is served buffet style so there is an option for everyone. You can also dine in the Savoyard themed restaurant which serves fondue, tartiflette and raclette - booking is required, just enquire with the reception team whilst you are away.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
